    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIRCAL\nSYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEffective April 1, 1981\nMIRCAL\nAIRCAL\nAIR CALIFORNIA\nIS NOW AIRCAL",
      "WINNING THE WEST WITH STYLE\nAIRCAL\nAIRCAL\nAir California has a fresh new name and a fresh\nnew style.\nThere's a new excitement in the air.\nYou can see it.\nYou can feel it.\nYou can fly it!\nAir California is now AirCal. And we're out to win the\nWest with style.\nWe have a new wardrobe that Mary McFadden\ndesigned for us. It is far from traditional and far and\naway the most innovative airline wardrobe you have\never seen.\nOur planes wear bold, progressive new AirCal\ncolors and once inside, you'll find relaxing; contem-\nporary interiors.\nAnother thing you'll find with AirCal is that we have\na way of doing things that will keep you flying with us\nagain and again. And that's style!"
    ],
